{"tid":2320534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國制裁17名外國官員　包括一名廈門公安","createTime":"2020-12-11T01:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T01:53:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":286,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"09233a5cc28572dddcb54e11275b3d4fb3bd8ca9","tid":2320534,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"美國制裁17名外國官員　包括一名廈門公安<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國國務院宣布制裁十七名，被指嚴重侵犯人權的外國官員及他們的直系家屬，包括一名中國公安人員，他被指嚴重侵犯法輪功成員的宗教自由。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院在周四國際人權日發聲明，制裁十七名外國現任及前官員，指他們嚴重侵犯人權及貪污腐敗，他們的直系家屬亦被列入制裁名單。<br />\n<br />\n被制裁的包括廈門市公安局思明分局梧村派出所主管黃元雄，他被指嚴重侵犯法輪功成員的宗教自由，他的太太亦被列入制裁名單，不能入境美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416170&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d7c041bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416170&h=85c53be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416170</a>"},{"pid":"e56c69d8e97b22e98b32ffc2fc4e06a2568fc233","tid":2320534,"uid":361751,"like":177,"dislike":2,"score":175,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"香港教育局楊潤雄大搞黨教育<br />\n<br />\n洗學生腦<br />\n<br />\n仲未制裁想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6056d0a6b3f49521bc5c84257a5c8c00bdab98a8","tid":2320534,"uid":236891,"like":177,"dislike":1,"score":176,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:49:15.000Z","msg":"他的太太亦被列入制裁名單，不能入境美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要制裁親人先有用"},{"pid":"c944a7b4fbecae4d31e3892786253f553ddaa76d","tid":2320534,"uid":176508,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:52:48.0